type-alias-py312
===============================================================================
Test Python 3.12 type alias syntax.
lang: python

--- file: src/lib.py ---

type Point = tuple[int, int]
type Vector = list[float]
type Callback = callable[[int], str]

def create_point(x: int, y: int) -> Point:
    return (x, y)

--- expect:block-graph ---
(root:1 lib ($TMP/src/lib.py)
